fastPathIscsiFlowAcceleration.name: fastPathIscsiFlowAcceleration

fastPathIscsiFlowAcceleration.description: The MIB definitions for Quality of Service - iSCSI Flow Acceleration Flex package.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationEnable.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationEnable
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationEnable.description: Enable/Disable iSCSI Flow Acceleration globally on the system.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationAgingTimeOut.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationAgingTimeOut
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationAgingTimeOut.description: The time in seconds that should pass before session is aged out after the last frame detected for the session.

QosType.name: QosType
QosType.description: Type of QoS: VPT or DSCP.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosType.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosType
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosType.description: Current type of QoS for iSCSI packets

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosVptValue.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosVptValue
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosVptValue.description: The value of VPT or DSCP, depends on agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosType, that will be assigned to each iSCSI packet. The range of VPT value is 0..7

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosDscpValue.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosDscpValue
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosDscpValue.description: The value of VPT or DSCP, depends on agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosType, that will be assigned to each iSCSI packet. The range of DSCP value is 0..63

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosRemark.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosRemark
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationQosRemark.description: Whether iSCSI frames with the configured VPT or DSCP when egressing the switch.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTa.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTable
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTa.description: The table for configuration of iSCSI target TCP port number, IP address, and name. It is indexed by agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTcpPort and agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigAddr.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigEn.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigEntry
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigEn.description: Row in the iSCSI Target configuration table.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTc.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTcpPort
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigTc.description: The TCP port of configured target.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigAd.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigAddr
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigAd.description: Specifies the target address. If the target address is to be ignored the address should be 0.0.0.0.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigNa.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigName
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigNa.description: The target IQN name. This text is not used to match on network traffic. It serves as an identifying comment for administrative convenience.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigSt.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigStatus
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationTargetConfigSt.description: The status of the target. It's used to add/delete a target. active(1) - this ACL instance is active createAndGo(4) - set to this value to create an instance destroy(6) - set to this value to delete an instance

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionTable.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionTable
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionTable.description: A table that contains iSCSI sessions. It is indexed as assigned by system.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionIndex.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionIndex
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionIndex.description: Numerical index of session table entry assigned by system.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessAgingTime.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessAgingTime
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessAgingTime.description: The elapsed time in seconds since the traffic was detected on any connections associated with this session.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionUpTime.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionUpTime
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionUpTime.description: Time elapsed since the session was detected, in seconds.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTabl.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTable
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTabl.description: A table that contains iSCSI connections. It is indexed as assigned by system.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionInde.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionIndex
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionInde.description: Numerical index of connection table entry assigned by system.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTarg.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTargetPort
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionTarg.description: The TCP port of connection target.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionInit.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionInitiatorPort
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionInit.description: The TCP port of connection initiator.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionCID.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionCID
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionCID.description: The iSCSI CID for this connection.

agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionSess.name: agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionSessionIndex
agentIscsiFlowAccelerationConnectionSess.description: The index of the session associated with this connection. Refers to the index of agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionIndex in agentIscsiFlowAccelerationSessionTable.
